---
description: AI agent and deterministic security scanner rules
globs:
  - "apps/agent/**/*"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Deterministic scanner services own facts, enrichment, scoring, and release decisions.
- OpenAI only explains structured data and formats remediation text.
- AI must not invent CVEs, versions, fixed versions, evidence, or release decisions.
- Include unknowns when enrichment or exact version data is incomplete.
- Keep behavior defensive only; no exploit code or offensive instructions.
- Unit tests must not call OpenAI or external networks.
